            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP S/4HANA</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-821916CC-3BD5-4C0E-965F-64E9B4198900" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/00577e8ec82b4cd19a411629b5529040</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="left" bottom="false" left="false" ref="text_name" right="true" top="false" valign="middle" x="68.0" y="29.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAC</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-EC8043D2-03D0-4F56-A0CE-C566C54B9BBD" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>When IP as customer ,In the standard order  SAC Will be the source of Pricing (Condition types ZCIP ,ZREV)
ZCIP Condition type will be used for Turnkey product Price
When there is a revenue by stage scenario applicable - Then Condition type ZREV will be applicable .</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-17F6C137-7079-457E-B6B7-3DE31EDC0AD1" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>IF Internal Transfer Price-Internal IF PO-SO scenario will follow Cost +Mark up Model
Cost is fetched from Material master .
Mark up ZM</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-CA201CCB-B968-409A-82E6-AF1723861A95" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Manual Upload of Pricing (Pricing for external customer- IF standard Pricing conditions </text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
